Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. One of your famous sayings is that love is beyond duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask, what is the fastest way to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You just realize that is innate to your own reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and just acknowledge that it is innate to that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you love like beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry? Oh, yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, love is only discovered where it's most intense and obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,very often interpersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after a while, you realize that you love life, you love nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you love all the kitties, you love all the doggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you love life, you know, the experience of life itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that you love life, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So lovingness, you identify with more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that it is already a reality and a capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and all you have to do is own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You love yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You love yourself right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You love yourself enough to come up in front of an audience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask a question, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just own that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you have to get or develop or acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It already exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,life should expire already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to write this one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't flub it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked this question for all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who are dealing with or trying to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilt and shame associated with masturbation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's come up a lot lately in conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to talk to you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That has a long history, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a long history and a biblical history
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the seven deadly sins is, you know, lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lust, lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself consider it, you know, relatively irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, it's not bringing harm to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So why is it decried in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why did mankind get into such a make-wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about it in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because lust then becomes an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,An attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a normal physiologic phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, nowadays people don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grew up, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,your father would leave you a book quietly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in your dresser drawer about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad didn't meet your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you missed a great book, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil, the evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of self-abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if you continue it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then they would describe somebody in a mental hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who was a feeble-minded idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that kind of book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And associated with syphilis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So somehow if you did that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you would end up feeble-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't stop doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and they had to put him in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So in those days, it was thought it led to insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I started at...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I started at a state hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not an inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a psychiatrist on the staff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at Manhattan State Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right under the Triborough Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And off the Triborough Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you can take an exit called Ward's Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you circle down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's an island underneath the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,right in the middle of New York City,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,completely removed from the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's its own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Manhattan State Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the state hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a lot of cases, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and their case history was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, some people have been there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,since, like, the 1920s, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then on the front of the chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it always gave you the probable cause of the disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would say self-abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's advanced schizophrenia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with massive personality deterioration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And the contributing or causative factor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was called the masturbation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So it led to insanity, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping me through that one, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's being trapped in sensuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the Buddha said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing you've got to let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is your attachment to sensual pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an attachment to sensuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,short-circuiting one's growth and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was greatly overplayed, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget, all that came out of the Victorian age,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when it was indecent to have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the naked leg of a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to have a drape over the leg of a table,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's very Victorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm trying to behave myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Victorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very Victorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all forms of sex were foreboding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Victorian era, except marital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you speak about transcending dualities?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can we talk about the generality of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than specifics?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've gotten through the one about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who's doing the healing work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,between the small self and the big self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's stuff coming up about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's identification with the initiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's seeing yourself as the source
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the initiator of volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't realize that these phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are happening of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the assumption
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a personal pronoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,me, a self,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as the doer and the originator and the decider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll realize,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if you keep looking at it and meditating on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's a narcissistic presumption
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and that no such entity exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you also talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that every thought that you come through your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is counted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, at another time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you've spoken about how the thoughts are not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we're not responsible for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At another time, wait a minute, don't jump around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At another time, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that the thoughts are not ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that the thoughts are happening on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're enlightened, they don't count anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you're not enlightened, they count plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you develop karma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To be enlightened is to be beyond karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are not the source of the author.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,These phenomena are happening of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness is happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no you, personal self,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that is doing this thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness is happening autonomously
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and spontaneously of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you presume that you're the author
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's on your TV set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then we're letting go of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Authorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The authorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena are happening of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't care a whit about you, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then to what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To what level are we responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for those thoughts that do come through?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, until you transcend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we let go of the authorship of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the purpose of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is to transcend karmic consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All those phenomena are happening of their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,including the presumption
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are originating from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, once you see through that hooker,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you get off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The presumption that you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a personal you causing all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is already an autonomous phenomena happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to mental insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my question is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been noticing that I get really stuck in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I analyze things to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I'm very analytical.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's lots of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and they just kind of keep going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I notice that it's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The basis, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,they're kind of masked by the question of why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is how to bypass it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and just be like, okay, you know, it just is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the mind gets enamored of its own thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets hypnotized by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it takes some subtlety of meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go the attraction of the pleasure of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as amusement,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as the feeling that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are doing something by...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or that you're getting some place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness can be let go as like a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessary to think at all, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everything is happening autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's the presumption that it's a requirement for life, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As I'm talking to you, I'm not giving this last thought
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness gets what the question is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the knowingness will respond, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,within the appropriate context, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's an addiction, let go of the thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see that all the purpose of thinkingness, amusement,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea that you're achieving goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're getting some place, that you're learning something, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a lot to let go of to transcend thinkingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it long lasts, the mind becomes silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you realize it always was silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is you doesn't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It witnesses thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then identifies it as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to you, but it isn't what you are, who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, meditate with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one time I had this experience where that seemed to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,where like there was less identification with the body and,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and like thoughts were just happening of their own and I was just watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and everything was really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there was just a change of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you get the sense of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you walk through the woods, the birds are singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not making them sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is shining, you're not making it shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaves are crunching on the grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not making them crunch on the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making anything happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Including being aware that you're walking through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say to yourself, gee, I wonder what I'm doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, I guess I must be walking through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You automatically know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the, the trick then is, is not to eliminate thoughts, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,stop verbalizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to turn it into language.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a nice day it is out here in the woods to see the squirrels playing with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the acorns in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, stop boring yourself with verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to verbalize about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly perfect day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say, oh my, what a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so trust in the autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quality that the mind has the, the capacity to get it in one instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets it, what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back with an update on my
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,daughter since we were here last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The demonic possessions have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They went away for ten days, and when they came back, it's no longer her being told
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She has not attempted that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, more so, the demons are telling her to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and it's pretty much constant every night in her sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the third psychiatrist that we went to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All were appropriate and integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one, over 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This first one, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one tried to institute, well, wanted to institutionalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, put her in a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, both of us, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the second one ended up not being appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to treat her epilepsy and said her psychosis was basically in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So this third psychiatrist has given us a new drug, but the possessions are still happening
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in that they're all, they're all directed at her killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what I ask of you now is, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe this doctor is appropriate, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she is integrous to treat my daughter, and that this new medication is an antipsychotic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as you suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's still not working, and it seemed to have heightened in that they don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,her to hurt anyone else but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point of, I did put bolts on my doors, but I went ahead and let her sleep with me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I could show her that I'm not afraid, that even if she does kill me, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you're going to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my karmic inheritance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what kind of medication is she on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Abilify.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was Risperdil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until seven days ago, it was Risperdil, and now it's Abilify.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a matter of adjusting doses, and some of these things take, and some of these take
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And sugar-free diet helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And big doses of vitamin B, B3 especially, and then the rest is a matter of time, a matter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She is terrified that she's going to get sent to the depths of hell like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She was at your last lecture, so she understands when you told that story, and she's juicing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that that's where she's going to end up if she kills herself or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I need to reassure her that she has the choice to ask God for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're treating a mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are slow to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to get the dose right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep raising the dose a little at a time until the symptoms should diminish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep raising the dose until you get out of the response you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get beyond that therapeutic threshold, you should see an improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw an improvement for 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've seen a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,improvement but when it plummeted it went right when it when it when it turned
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,back around in the position started it was magnified a new wave 10 intensified
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I can tell you is you try a one or two different medications but within the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,same class of anti-psychotics then you adjust the dose if you don't get a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,recovery on half a milligram a day of prolixin you go to one milligram if you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get it on that you go to two milligrams I mean you know it's just a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:19:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,matter of professional skill doctors don't like to be told what to do what
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,when I've suggested prolixin or something like it I've been met with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,contempt except for the last doctor they've all told me well it's an old drug
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there's newer better ones so I guess there's no better ones but I just gave
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that as an example yes sir all right so then it's a matter of adjusting the dose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to find the therapeutic range
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time I was here I think Andrea and you both and dr. Kallenbach but what
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt to express was my gratitude to the hundreds of people that have been in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your lecture so what I get right now is that because your mother Mia hold your
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,hand and I wanted to tell you thank you for helping me yeah and believing in me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all right now here's what you do is try to talk them into going to a higher dose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a man or a lady, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm willing to take the risk of a higher dose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's a certain therapeutic range,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and you may get nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and then once you break through a therapeutic range,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly the whole thing will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would let her know you're willing to experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with maybe stronger doses, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to at least eliminate that as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But very often, the psychosis will prevail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on half a milligram a day or something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get up to three-quarter or one milligram disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can be just below the therapeutic threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to work with psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are really so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how they stay in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,every patient is a research project, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what combination of meds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and what dosages they're going to respond to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hang out at one milligram
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they stay completely psychotic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and at two milligrams,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole thing disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So why not experiment and go up to two milligrams
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and see what the heck happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When the dosage is right, I get my daughter back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When the dose is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we have great hopes that the phenomenon will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So trying to get a doctor who's willing to go along with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, you know, I'm not going to be able to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,until we've tried maybe a stronger dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're clear on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Any patient doesn't get better on one dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You go a little higher and they go random remissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about a sentence in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is best to speak to the inner conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and commit it to becoming a useful ally and teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than a sadistic self-perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I made such an intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't think it listened very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ego is sadistic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets pleasure out of punishing you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and causing you pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to deprive it of that pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and teach it that it's being wicked by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you clarify, teach it that it's being wicked?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you clarify that a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I teach it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I teach it that it's being wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I'm talking to it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you talk to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, the conscience is supposed to be your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,not your tormentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not supposed to be your prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or persecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a helpful guide between right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't give it full reign or that much credence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:23:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because it isn't all that smart to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one more quick question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is hypnotherapy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tegress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give your superego a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't ask you to become a sadist or a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to talk to it like a Dutch uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the superego is one's incorporated parental voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold is listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The superego is one's internalized parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.57,0:24:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gives you a different way to deal with this overzealous parent
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.74,0:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,who's overdoing his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.98,0:24:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk to it like an overzealous parent, like you're a counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.62,0:24:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be a guide, not a crucifier or a punisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.64,0:24:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.96,0:24:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to talk it into being more rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.64,0:24:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.36,0:24:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.86,0:24:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get rough with them once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.76,0:25:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dutch uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to put up with abuse from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.05,0:25:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We value your guidance, but not your abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.77,0:25:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.01,0:25:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, when I came across your teaching a couple of years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.07,0:25:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reasonably reclusive, and I thought would become more so,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually becoming more and more active and extrovert and out in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.19,0:25:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been more enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.99,0:25:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And my prayer for the last many months has been, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.37,0:25:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be able to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be able to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.31,0:25:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And my prayer for the last many months has been to be more committed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.79,0:25:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to the path of devotion and truth in that process so that that would be there in activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.45,0:25:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to state that prayer in your presence out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.81,0:25:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.43,0:25:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.72,0:25:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with what you were saying about marketing this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.32,0:25:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And previously, marketing is usually on the level of 100 and 125.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.76,0:25:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is how to do marketing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.06,0:25:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in an integral way?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.76,0:25:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.92,0:26:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do marketing in an integral way?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.41,0:26:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Marketing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.89,0:26:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.35,0:26:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You were talking about advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.01,0:26:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.33,0:26:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Advertising, a few of them know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.53,0:26:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of them seem to be totally blind to what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.84,0:26:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Some ads are attractive and enhance the project, their product, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.07,0:26:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take Geico, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.33,0:26:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing cuter than the Geico guy walking around and all the Geico ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.77,0:26:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Geico, Geico, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.39,0:26:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, it's Geico.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.37,0:26:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is kind of, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a Geico.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.83,0:26:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a Geico for Geico.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there are some products that by sheer repetition
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.02,0:26:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dumbness of the advertisement create an aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.86,0:26:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't realize that they're creating an aversion to their product.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.19,0:27:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.89,0:27:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never liked the A-flag duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.59,0:27:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, there's a bank and a banking firm that comes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.25,0:27:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm glad to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.39,0:27:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see they've taken big losses in this last dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.15,0:27:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.57,0:27:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this idiot comes on with his rap.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.27,0:27:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the advertisement immediately turns out and immediately replays itself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.05,0:27:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to do advertising in an integrous ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.36,0:27:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, integrous means a little bit different in advertising than, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.76,0:27:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the person says they've recovered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.26,0:27:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're not using such and such a product.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.98,0:27:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're lying or not convincing, they get an actor or an actress to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.34,0:27:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, how so-and-so cured my acne.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.92,0:27:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She never had acne, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.78,0:27:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.64,0:27:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So there isn't the ring of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.24,0:27:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of truth is not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.88,0:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want somebody who actually recovered from an actual disease
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.94,0:28:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that was making your life miserable with this product.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.58,0:28:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now when he tells me, you know, that solved my acne, I believe the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.20,0:28:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I used to be a pimply mess, and now the girl's all smiling at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.67,0:28:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So it should be truthful to be convincing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.05,0:28:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because the energy field of a lie is below 200 is not very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.86,0:28:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then some of them just suffer from sheer lack of IQ on the part of the designers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.54,0:28:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also thought it would be great fun to show people how to get more for your money,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.84,0:28:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because they spend big money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.91,0:28:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And to me, they get a poor return on their money, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.93,0:28:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the process of creating advertising and marketing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.45,0:28:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.97,0:28:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering what some of you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.05,0:28:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.29,0:28:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are some of your suggestions might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.47,0:28:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.49,0:28:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a real fun thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.23,0:28:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, various parts of an ad may create a version.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.69,0:28:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This part of the ad is attractive, but this part of the ad creates an aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.83,0:28:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have people look at the various parts of the ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.73,0:28:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And calibrate the energy of it, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.11,0:29:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think marketing would be great fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.69,0:29:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see people get more miles for their dollar, because they put big money there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.56,0:29:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the company that puts on the ad, I mean, they don't care what's,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.92,0:29:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the content of the ad, because they're getting paid so much per minute, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.48,0:29:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.28,0:29:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.50,0:29:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a fun thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.94,0:29:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been through some serious trauma recently, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.14,0:29:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my life as a total, it's getting to a peak right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.81,0:29:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like if I don't do something to semi-heal myself to an extent,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.82,0:29:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm going to fall too far to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.40,0:29:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if you have any advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:29:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of trauma are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.14,0:30:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've had a lot of family issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.92,0:30:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been homeless on and off for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.53,0:30:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been abused for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.75,0:30:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.93,0:30:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any working relationships right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.53,0:30:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.15,0:30:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You got friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.99,0:30:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.41,0:30:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.35,0:30:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have things working to the best they've been in about six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.41,0:30:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.71,0:30:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to figure out what was my next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.01,0:30:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is the best bet for me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As regards what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.26,0:30:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To come to some kind of realization of what terms I need to keep to keep myself from slipping back or...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.96,0:30:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slipping back to what? Robbing banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.70,0:30:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Something, no, something that I can't, no, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.68,0:30:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.26,0:30:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like feelings of suicide or feelings that I just am too deep in despair to do anything with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.18,0:30:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like depression, is that what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or drugs or whatever it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.66,0:30:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about depression?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.66,0:30:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.10,0:30:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a serious problem with depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.52,0:30:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you taking any antidepressants?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.84,0:31:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they won't put me on antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.28,0:31:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first of all, I'm very sensitive to the medications.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.90,0:31:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I take the antidepressants, the stimulant in them kind of makes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.06,0:31:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Agitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.46,0:31:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Too up to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.36,0:31:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.72,0:31:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.74,0:31:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.72,0:31:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.72,0:31:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then it's a matter of working on yourself psychologically, being in every kind of therapy you can be, individual and group.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.02,0:31:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Any 12-step groups you belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done that for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.40,0:31:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.62,0:31:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't belong to any right now because I just moved, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.84,0:31:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.92,0:31:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to get back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's all you can do is a total push.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.46,0:31:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, whatever medications work the best, whatever 12-step groups, recovery groups, associating with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.08,0:31:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do for an occupation?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.72,0:31:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You work?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.02,0:31:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not lately, but I've worked many, many, many jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.92,0:31:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.42,0:31:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.06,0:31:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you working?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.98,0:31:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you on, welfare or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.34,0:31:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have money in the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.64,0:31:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.14,0:32:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was left in inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.64,0:32:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was left in inheritance, actually, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.68,0:32:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you and I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.74,0:32:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got great therapeutic plans for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.06,0:32:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.06,0:32:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.76,0:32:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.17,0:32:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you joy in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.75,0:32:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You got anything that brings you joy besides feeling sorry for yourself and giving me a sad story?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.23,0:32:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I like music.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.99,0:32:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I like videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.95,0:32:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I like movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.99,0:32:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.47,0:32:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.23,0:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You like dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.27,0:32:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You like to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.35,0:32:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.19,0:32:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.85,0:32:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take up dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.87,0:32:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.21,0:32:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's how he does dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.55,0:32:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.79,0:32:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You like dancing and movies, and usually you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.45,0:32:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.95,0:32:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you got friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.11,0:32:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.85,0:32:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way ahead of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.48,0:32:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.18,0:32:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at that point where I need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.22,0:32:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.52,0:33:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's either this time I decide to really get it done and make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.66,0:33:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.86,0:33:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either do I take the step or do I not take the step.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.38,0:33:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you volunteer for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.53,0:33:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in a long time, but I used to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.45,0:33:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.59,0:33:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to remember, but I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.45,0:33:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Try volunteering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.03,0:33:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Try volunteering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.53,0:33:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in your life is meaningful?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.35,0:33:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in your life is meaningful?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.78,0:33:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I feel my life is meaningful?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.80,0:33:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.26,0:33:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel my life is meaningful, but I know my life is meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.10,0:33:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like it is, but I know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.90,0:33:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.14,0:33:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So in what situation do you feel best?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.96,0:33:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like she asked you about working with animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.87,0:33:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.59,0:33:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two puppies right now, but they're at my ex-roommate's house, who is just a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.47,0:33:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,horrible person as far as anything's concerned, and I'd love to work at Community Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need to take care of my puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.74,0:33:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do, and it's just, I'll figure something out that gives me direction
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.32,0:33:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to head, thinking to volunteer at the Community Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.40,0:33:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.68,0:34:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're working your way through this swamp slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.88,0:34:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.28,0:34:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not as bad as you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.86,0:34:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.24,0:34:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The depression's not quite as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.18,0:34:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost overwhelmed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.44,0:34:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.54,0:34:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.80,0:34:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.42,0:34:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the only thing you can do is pharmacologically, I think we could do better with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.86,0:34:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.74,0:34:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not satisfied with the pharmacologic results.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.22,0:34:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.64,0:34:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the whole business...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.02,0:34:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole business has not really been worked on yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.74,0:34:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.26,0:34:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as what I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.36,0:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need a good psychopharmacologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.80,0:34:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not satisfied with what the medications are doing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.80,0:34:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.56,0:34:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be just dilapidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.18,0:34:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.12,0:34:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Discombobulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.26,0:34:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.72,0:34:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a doctor you're working with?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.43,0:34:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.17,0:34:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.46,0:34:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a psychiatrist, yeah, but I see him like once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.16,0:34:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me Risperdal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.80,0:34:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on Risperdal constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.90,0:34:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I got off Risperdal constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.10,0:34:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he gave me Risperdal pills, 0.5 twice a day, and I haven't taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.76,0:35:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken them for three days, two days ago, and now I'm coming off of them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming off of what again?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.92,0:35:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Risperdal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Risperdal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.22,0:35:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.60,0:35:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Risperdal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.24,0:35:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an antidepressant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.48,0:35:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's an antipsychotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.52,0:35:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you take for an antidepressant?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.18,0:35:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken Welbutrin, which gave me the 2% to 3% that people have anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.46,0:35:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got extreme anxiety from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.30,0:35:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.76,0:35:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't prescribe Welbutrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.85,0:35:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoloft.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.41,0:35:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoloft made me too hyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.83,0:35:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.47,0:35:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.95,0:35:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.23,0:35:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have ADD and ADHD, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.45,0:35:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.19,0:35:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.82,0:35:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you're a project.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.75,0:35:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.30,0:35:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A multifaceted project.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.30,0:35:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.48,0:35:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You work on all of them with patience, and at the other end, there's a light at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.93,0:35:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.05,0:35:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.77,0:35:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.31,0:35:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of patience, and work your way through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.75,0:35:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.31,0:35:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do all the things that you know will be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.89,0:35:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.21,0:35:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Having friends is a very important part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.47,0:35:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.75,0:35:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.25,0:35:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.40,0:35:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.74,0:36:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've made good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.68,0:36:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.78,0:36:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.28,0:36:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.68,0:36:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.32,0:36:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.86,0:36:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.14,0:36:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.91,0:36:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.57,0:36:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Things were worse before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.49,0:36:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.13,0:36:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.16,0:36:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the death and dying video, you mentioned a horrible mistake that you had made that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.68,0:36:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,condemned you to a thousand years of guilt and inability to enjoy dancing and things
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.40,0:36:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.66,0:36:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.83,0:36:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Either too close or too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.71,0:36:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.29,0:36:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.75,0:36:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.01,0:36:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.09,0:36:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In the death and dying video.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.25,0:36:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the microphone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.43,0:36:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.13,0:36:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.47,0:36:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.91,0:36:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In the death and dying video, office series.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.99,0:36:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.51,0:36:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that you had made a horrible mistake that self-condemned you to many,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.67,0:37:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,many lifetimes of guilt and therefore an inability to enjoy joy, like dancing, things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.77,0:37:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.83,0:37:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.61,0:37:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.71,0:37:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was this mistake that you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.91,0:37:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the mistake you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.34,0:37:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.99,0:37:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.25,0:37:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.15,0:37:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it hurt 10 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.27,0:37:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember where it hurt 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.84,0:37:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is it doesn't hurt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.36,0:37:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.28,0:37:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.88,0:37:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was thinking so that others could potentially avoid it if you remembered it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.88,0:37:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.64,0:37:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I don't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.70,0:37:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.64,0:37:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.28,0:37:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it could be something like killing the wrong person, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.50,0:37:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't the guy my wife was having an affair with after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.50,0:37:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.22,0:37:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.45,0:38:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is hypno...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.75,0:38:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since you don't know that one, can I just ask another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.43,0:38:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Different one?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.44,0:38:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.06,0:38:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.70,0:38:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know hypnagogia or hypnagogia?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.28,0:38:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.72,0:38:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnagogic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.46,0:38:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.74,0:38:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.44,0:38:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.64,0:38:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those experiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.60,0:38:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnagogic is an altered state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.56,0:38:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A hypnotic-like state.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.71,0:38:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnagogic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.07,0:38:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnagogic hallucinations, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.33,0:38:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.41,0:38:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,People have them right before they fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.79,0:38:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll suddenly have like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.28,0:38:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they'll wake up in a hypnagogic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.28,0:38:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.28,0:38:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.04,0:38:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.14,0:38:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the significance of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.34,0:38:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.68,0:38:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.28,0:38:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a physiologic reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.11,0:38:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like some people sleepwalk, a lot of people don't, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.59,0:38:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.29,0:38:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.42,0:38:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.98,0:39:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.17,0:39:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.10,0:39:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For three years, we've been studying all of your books at my university in classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.38,0:39:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And just watching what happens at the University of Redlands in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.23,0:39:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've known enough to assign your books, turn on some classical music, and get the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.61,0:39:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,hell out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.75,0:39:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I realize the semester's starting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.03,0:39:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's coming up is really wanting to, in your presence, and yours, Susan, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.43,0:39:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,group.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.53,0:39:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Too close to the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.19,0:39:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.39,0:39:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.50,0:39:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's coming up as the new semester is starting is to wanting in the presence of you two and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.94,0:40:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,these people that I love so much, even though I don't know hardly any of their names, is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.02,0:40:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to dedicate all the studies that happen there, everything that is part of my work, to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.20,0:40:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to my love for you, and to the truth, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.94,0:40:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And to the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.70,0:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And to the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.40,0:40:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like what happens there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.16,0:40:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is part of what happens here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.78,0:40:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a real blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.30,0:40:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.56,0:40:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.42,0:40:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.46,0:40:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.34,0:40:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.00,0:40:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You already are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.34,0:40:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.86,0:40:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.38,0:40:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.00,0:40:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.24,0:40:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said this morning that the best thing we can do is to dedicate our lives to our
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:40:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,fellow man and to God as we understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.34,0:40:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.90,0:40:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.50,0:41:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I would like you to elaborate on as we understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.54,0:41:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your comprehension, understanding God varies at various stages of your evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So to serve yourself, serve your fellow man, and serve God simultaneously fulfills all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.70,0:41:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.94,0:41:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All the possibilities, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.45,0:41:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And serving God as you understand him means, however you might conceive of it, being, you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.11,0:41:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,know, the most loving way you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.56,0:41:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't have to try and understand him at a higher level and...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.02,0:41:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to understand God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.66,0:41:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not going to understand God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.90,0:41:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.66,0:41:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.66,0:41:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So just where I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.88,0:41:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I'm at with my relationship with divinity is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.10,0:41:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.56,0:41:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To serve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.40,0:41:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever you're at with it is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.64,0:41:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.40,0:41:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.98,0:41:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.00,0:41:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God will give you a beefer effort, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.58,0:42:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I just want to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.52,0:42:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to express my gratitude to both of you for your devotion to being devoted
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.64,0:42:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to us and to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.70,0:42:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.65,0:42:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like we all have our own little personal subjective bubble that sort of seems personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.11,0:42:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever comes into that, we're prone to identifying with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.46,0:42:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound about right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.00,0:42:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.96,0:42:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.34,0:42:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.77,0:42:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.64,0:42:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You got another question.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.27,0:42:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.63,0:42:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see if I had it figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.33,0:42:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.19,0:42:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.37,0:42:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.49,0:42:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever comes into the bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.85,0:42:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.51,0:42:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.73,0:43:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For enlightened beings who remain in this world, are they accountable for their body,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.41,0:43:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what their body does?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.30,0:43:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Accountable?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.60,0:43:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is who accountable?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.97,0:43:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it wouldn't even be a question to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.72,0:43:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did enlightened beings fall back into a small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.28,0:43:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can enlightened beings fall back into a small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.97,0:43:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How can enlightened beings fall back into a small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.99,0:43:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How can enlightened beings fall back into a small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.57,0:43:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can enlightened beings fall back into a small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.27,0:43:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did an enlightened being fall into what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.73,0:43:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did an enlightened being fall back into what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.27,0:43:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did an enlightened being fall back into what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.77,0:43:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Into a small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.27,0:43:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Into a separate small self?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.39,0:43:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How did enlightened beings calibrate above 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.71,0:43:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,fall back down into a state of duality?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.29,0:43:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, because not every person who reaches a high level
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.97,0:43:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is sufficiently evolved to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.99,0:44:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still defects, still defects, vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.04,0:44:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.60,0:44:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.78,0:44:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.06,0:44:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.42,0:44:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.52,0:44:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.76,0:44:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.00,0:44:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.04,0:44:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in my opinion, it's the fault of their teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.62,0:44:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that didn't warn of what could happen at these various levels
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.72,0:44:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and what to watch out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.85,0:44:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing, when you hit a high level,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.27,0:44:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual ego wants to take over right away
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.89,0:44:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, oh, look how marvelous I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.28,0:44:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be the great teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.68,0:44:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and be on all the television programs and write books and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So the vanity of the ego then wants to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.55,0:44:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the problem there is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.23,0:44:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there's still the illusion of a personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.99,0:44:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the illusion of a personal self disappears,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.37,0:44:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then the great vulnerability tends to disappear, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.51,0:44:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that means enlightened teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.27,0:44:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not there permanently yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.32,0:44:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and they still have vulnerability,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.80,0:44:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,residual tendency to identify with a small self.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.94,0:44:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.30,0:44:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There still may be a defect, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:44:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So a person may go into a very high state
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.46,0:45:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then succumb to a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.08,0:45:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the evil spirits the Buddha described.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.72,0:45:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was attacked by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.49,0:45:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Start looking around to see where you're vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.24,0:45:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about fame?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.70,0:45:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a little roll in the hay, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.56,0:45:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They just keep feeling you out
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.06,0:45:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,until they see, my gosh, I think you're a wonderful teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.90,0:45:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm a wonderful teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.04,0:45:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So influencing others, having many followers,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.91,0:45:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,mega church,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.67,0:45:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've got 50,000 followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make you more knowledgeable?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.04,0:45:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it makes you a charismatic character.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.52,0:45:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So each of these things has its own vulnerability, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.10,0:45:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people through good fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.52,0:45:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of good karma
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.92,0:45:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have any open gates like that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.47,0:45:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for anything to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.35,0:45:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people have been taught in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.83,0:45:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and forewarned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.07,0:46:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had very close relationships with teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.97,0:46:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and watched them crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.58,0:46:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw it coming, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.54,0:46:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.50,0:46:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a vulnerability all the way up to 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.36,0:46:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.43,0:46:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's up to 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.43,0:46:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.99,0:46:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance for error,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.85,0:46:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not a vulnerability to something from out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.65,0:46:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the trap of the void at 850, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.46,0:46:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you realize that there's something beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.20,0:46:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to think that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.52,0:46:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to have a very advanced teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.87,0:46:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that tells you of the traps along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.21,0:46:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and outlines the stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.87,0:46:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside and the downside of each of those levels, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.92,0:46:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So for the last doorway,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.68,0:46:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when the illusion of one is the source of one's life died
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.46,0:46:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcend,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.32,0:46:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is there more gates to go through after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.12,0:46:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.14,0:47:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.46,0:47:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because you'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.33,0:47:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.70,0:47:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.09,0:47:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the you that's worried about it won't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.02,0:47:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no you left to worry about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.64,0:47:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God's worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.94,0:47:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to figure out how to make this microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.92,0:47:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,work a little better, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.60,0:47:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.96,0:47:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.62,0:47:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just simply came to ask for your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.00,0:47:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.98,0:47:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.16,0:47:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.54,0:47:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.16,0:47:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.52,0:47:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see your own self shining forth back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.06,0:47:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you're seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.22,0:48:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.17,0:48:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The beauty and perfection of the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.35,0:48:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you are, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.13,0:48:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.20,0:48:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.54,0:48:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.40,0:48:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,why did humanity fall from non-duality to duality?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.18,0:48:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have to ask God that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.85,0:48:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.50,0:48:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Garden of Eden,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.02,0:48:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the serpent came along and tempted Eve, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.71,0:48:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And my feeling is that it was her innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.41,0:48:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Her vulnerability was her innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.88,0:49:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The trustiness of the inner child.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.53,0:49:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the serpent knows that the weakness of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.93,0:49:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.53,0:49:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, little girl, and I'll show you how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.74,0:49:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the serpent seduced her where he knew she was not conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.86,0:49:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and not defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.44,0:49:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the only defense she had was if she had bided it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.74,0:49:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by God's edict to obey the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.81,0:49:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's said that it was due to disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.75,0:49:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.35,0:49:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.01,0:49:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The obedience was a way of protecting her
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.89,0:49:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from the ignorance and the vulnerability of her innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.74,0:49:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you tell a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.90,0:49:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,don't walk across the street without holding my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.84,0:49:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the child in innocence thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.36,0:49:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if he walks across the street, the cars will put the brake on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.39,0:49:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So the only thing that protects the child
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.21,0:50:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the authoritative statement of the parent
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.02,0:50:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,until the child's own sense of reality grows up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.14,0:50:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and sees that you can't walk across the street
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.02,0:50:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.40,0:50:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, there's only the authority of the parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.87,0:50:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So Eve's innocence was her vulnerability,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.03,0:50:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and her current defect was a disobedience to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.91,0:50:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which would have protected her against the vulnerability
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.49,0:50:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of her narcissistic ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.78,0:50:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.14,0:50:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said was absolute fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.86,0:50:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.06,0:50:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said is factually so.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.48,0:50:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's my understanding of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.62,0:50:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't throw her out of the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.98,0:50:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.77,0:50:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've talked about the difference between salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.61,0:51:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and enlightenment and how the Lord Christ taught for salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.97,0:51:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and Buddha taught about enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.81,0:51:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Course in Miracles, I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.97,0:51:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at about 600, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.77,0:51:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.59,0:51:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.13,0:51:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't 600 the first level of enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.83,0:51:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.47,0:51:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So then the Course in Miracles is really teaching both salvation and enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.26,0:51:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.26,0:51:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.26,0:51:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read it in many a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.26,0:51:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.26,0:51:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the impression...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.26,0:51:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any difference, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.26,0:51:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.26,0:51:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you turn down salvation for enlightenment, or turn down enlightenment for salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.06,0:51:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think of salvation as one of the stages before...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.06,0:51:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is already salvation, and salvation is already enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.06,0:51:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just two different pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.06,0:51:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're terminologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.06,0:51:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.06,0:51:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.82,0:51:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.06,0:51:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, salvation was prior to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.54,0:52:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, enlightenment is in itself salvation, but not of a design such as salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.82,0:52:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, with salvation, one has a savior who speaks for you before God as your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.72,0:52:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that word?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.72,0:52:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I always forget that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.72,0:52:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As your...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.65,0:52:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.65,0:52:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.65,0:52:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.65,0:52:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.65,0:52:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.57,0:52:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.57,0:52:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That would not come to the mind of the Buddha to need an advocate, having become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.61,0:52:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.06,0:52:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.22,0:52:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.22,0:52:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.22,0:52:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.22,0:52:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.22,0:52:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get stuck there, give me a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.22,0:52:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.22,0:52:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lens cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.22,0:52:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.22,0:52:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I always forget that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.44,0:52:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.50,0:53:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it in German, but not in English.
