Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.58,0:55:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel happy with it well that's that's uh all there is to it isn't it is there anything more
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.12,0:55:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing else i can think of okay i have a general question also yeah um how do you know when um you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.64,0:56:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,understand something intellectually or when you like an intellectual understanding or is it like a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.20,0:56:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,subjective um understanding yeah it's experiential it's experiential and uh
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.23,0:56:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you can understand it intellectually but not experientially or vice versa
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.14,0:56:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can understand them uh both both ways simultaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.10,0:56:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,okay so how do i know when i'm having a subjective um experience like where i have an
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.38,0:56:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a real subjective understanding of your teachings or is it uh intellectualized understanding well
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.26,0:56:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the both both go together you know st thomas aquinas says you know that reason reinforces
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.34,0:56:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,faith and that faith illuminates what reason uh illuminates reason so you can intellectually
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.53,0:57:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,understand the thing but its true meaning is only a revelation which comes out of accompanying it by
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.60,0:57:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,faith though faith and reason go hand in hand see okay yeah faith the reason go hand in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.24,0:57:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can understand the thing and then ask god for a miracle to really fully
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.68,0:57:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,realize, what does that really fully mean
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.74,0:57:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in its totality?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.57,0:57:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't get an answer, complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.10,0:57:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I'm shaking the gates of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.98,0:57:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.74,0:57:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the answer comes forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.78,0:57:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason plus faith is the great
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.44,0:57:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.10,0:57:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Thomas Aquinas was a
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.52,0:57:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor of divinity. He was a doctor of the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.48,0:57:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,church, and about as good as you can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.22,0:57:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, congratulations to the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.62,0:57:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.26,0:57:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They owe us a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.26,0:58:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pay you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.14,0:58:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, God bless you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.62,0:58:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.84,0:58:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.43,0:58:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so many couples that met in that class
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.73,0:58:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.03,0:58:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get to stack up the couples that met
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.63,0:58:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and got married in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.12,0:58:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.08,0:58:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Aquinas. Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.82,0:58:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.98,0:58:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.20,0:58:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.95,0:58:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,15. I was really
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.89,0:58:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,excited because I told a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.11,0:58:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what all my problems are.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.69,0:58:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to solve all my problems. If I can give up
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.95,0:58:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing, I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.03,0:58:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,have any problems anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.59,0:58:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And she
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.95,0:58:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,thought I was crazy, and so
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.03,0:58:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just dropped it. I forgot about it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.69,0:58:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,until 25 years later when I found your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.89,0:58:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I remembered that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.25,0:58:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or that I had that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.91,0:58:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,memory of that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.05,0:58:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.60,0:58:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.20,0:59:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've been working on
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.74,0:59:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,practicing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.12,0:59:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering experience
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.85,0:59:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.71,0:59:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,then I came to a place
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.77,0:59:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.93,0:59:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,was peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.46,0:59:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I started
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.26,0:59:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming like
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.66,0:59:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not having any emotion, like very
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.00,0:59:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.80,0:59:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember you telling somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.88,0:59:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,during one of the lectures that that's very normal
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.18,0:59:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,part of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.04,0:59:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I let that go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.78,0:59:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have a fear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.92,0:59:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,arising of not existing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.00,0:59:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,at all. So if I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.14,0:59:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,attached to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.58,0:59:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have this fear of not
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.17,0:59:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,existing, then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.27,0:59:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I move backwards
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.91,0:59:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like when I have that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.70,0:59:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.46,0:59:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing. You're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.84,0:59:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,fear. Yeah, yeah, yeah. That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.94,0:59:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I move backwards when I
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.46,0:59:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when the fear arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.10,0:59:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let go. Wind the track.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.20,1:00:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go. Wind the controller.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.58,1:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And look more
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.26,1:00:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to the presence of God as
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.14,1:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,love, as love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.60,1:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of love. See?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.39,1:00:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because love is an
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.79,1:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness. It's not really experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.65,1:00:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.32,1:00:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can transcend the sort of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.22,1:00:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,void that you're going through
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.86,1:00:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,by focusing on the infinite reality
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.20,1:00:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity itself to the core
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.84,1:00:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.01,1:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And affirm love as
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.01,1:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a basic quality of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.99,1:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my confusion
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.45,1:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,was because I have
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.39,1:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,had an experience of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.65,1:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the celestial realm and the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.29,1:00:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,overwhelming, unspeakable
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.45,1:00:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,love that, can you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.64,1:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,speak? Yes, yes. So I was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.38,1:00:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,confused about experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.14,1:00:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because that was an experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.54,1:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're saying it's an experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.36,1:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You're saying it's
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.94,1:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,an experience. That it was just a being.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.52,1:00:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a state. You know, experiencing was something
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.90,1:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're tacking on to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.68,1:01:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So. It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.98,1:01:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.42,1:01:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is of its own. See?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.18,1:01:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need to experience it to confirm
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.32,1:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a reality or existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.22,1:01:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tag on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.59,1:01:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rainy thunderous day.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.59,1:01:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need I experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.39,1:01:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it as such for it to be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.37,1:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know? Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.20,1:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tag. It's an add-on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.70,1:01:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let go of the add-on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.60,1:01:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. And
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.14,1:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're going through is not that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.36,1:01:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,hard to go through. It's not hard
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.50,1:01:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to go through. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.86,1:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seems puzzling at
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.10,1:01:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the time. But it's actually
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.04,1:01:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not that hard. It's much
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.34,1:01:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,harder to get beyond the lower levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.25,1:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Higher levels are
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.39,1:01:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe dumbfounding, but
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.70,1:01:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they're relatively easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.82,1:01:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They suddenly resolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.12,1:01:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So the confusion
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.86,1:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is normal then? Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.68,1:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all. The confusion is coming from trying to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.80,1:02:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it. You can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.00,1:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Not understandable.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.44,1:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.53,1:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.01,1:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to understand it. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.07,1:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.87,1:02:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God get you through it. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.15,1:02:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Help God. Help God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.36,1:02:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.20,1:02:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on this side of the garden gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.54,1:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me through the garden gate, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.14,1:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? I started a study
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.75,1:02:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,group in Madison, Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.49,1:02:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And for
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.79,1:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,six months, nobody showed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.07,1:02:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But then
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.87,1:02:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,she showed up, and
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.33,1:02:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we got married last month.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.67,1:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.65,1:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to end up as Mary and Sam
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.51,1:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.77,1:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.95,1:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.11,1:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With that cartoon, Mary and Sam.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.49,1:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.37,1:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, what are some
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.05,1:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,things we could do to protect ourselves from
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.97,1:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the media barrage
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.39,1:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of the programming?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.21,1:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sophistication,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.29,1:03:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,for one thing, what we
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.99,1:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,talked about this morning, already
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.57,1:03:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,guards you against it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.58,1:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.76,1:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hold all information
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.28,1:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as provisional. There is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.22,1:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,no final information out there. Everything
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.12,1:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is provisional. You know, all the records of World
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.36,1:03:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,War II, now some of them are turning out to be false,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.78,1:03:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, 25, 50 years later.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.87,1:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So all information is provisional at the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.85,1:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So wisdom means to hold all, everything that you learn,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.06,1:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as provisional. That's the way it seems now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.71,1:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. We only recently learned from Professor,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.46,1:04:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget his name now, that Japan was very close to
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.93,1:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,their own nuclear bomb. And if we hadn't dropped it, they would have dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.73,1:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They would have dropped it on us. They were very close.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.15,1:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was only revealed in 1992 or 94, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.92,1:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's many years after the event. And even now, we just, we suddenly get the information.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.04,1:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He was on television and we got to interview him and talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.39,1:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They were, if we hadn't dropped it, they were going to drop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.65,1:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're going to drop it very shortly, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.99,1:04:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What I've been kind of doing is avoiding watching television just because, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.65,1:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I find myself getting sucked into the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.43,1:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,dramas and the things. Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.43,1:04:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just like, oh, here I go again. And so I've, I've kind of been...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.19,1:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a detached amusement. When you watch a cartoon, you don't have to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.95,1:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the cartoon. Mickey Mouse is real and he's going to come in your backyard. To me, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.88,1:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,like Mickey Mouse. What's Mickey Mouse saying here tonight, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.37,1:05:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. It's a game, a conversational game.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.59,1:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have... Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.59,1:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your, close it up on the thing and then everyone will know it was caused by a nuclear
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.14,1:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,bomb. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.07,1:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.86,1:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, give it to Scott right down there in the front.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.86,1:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.86,1:05:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.99,1:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.99,1:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll put it up and then you'll have more.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.99,1:05:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my father was very well known at the University of Madison. Red Hawkins Band
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.99,1:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,was a university band for many years. And so Madison is the old Rathskeller and it was
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.99,1:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,really in Lake Mendota and all the frat houses and sorority houses.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.99,1:05:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get a blessing, a marital blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.99,1:05:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you got a blessing. Yes, indeed. God bless you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.99,1:05:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.99,1:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.99,1:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.99,1:05:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.99,1:05:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.99,1:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.54,1:05:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.54,1:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.54,1:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.54,1:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.54,1:05:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.54,1:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.54,1:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.05,1:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.05,1:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.05,1:05:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.05,1:05:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.05,1:05:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.05,1:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.11,1:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.37,1:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.37,1:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the family, love and blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.37,1:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed. God bless you both. God's happiness be yours. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.09,1:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.09,1:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a charming couple.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.10,1:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Madison, Wisconsin, can you believe that, huh? I can tell you some wild stories about
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.32,1:06:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Madison.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.32,1:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.26,1:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,bird went poop.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.26,1:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The vial.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.48,1:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The beard.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.48,1:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.48,1:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.71,1:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten cents.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.71,1:06:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.71,1:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I make up the last third of the Madison, Wisconsin contingent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.99,1:06:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.99,1:06:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.99,1:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,except the last third of the Madison list.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.58,1:06:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.22,1:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, yes, I get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.48,1:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to come to receive your grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.60,1:06:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.82,1:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.28,1:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless your way in this world,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.84,1:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.92,1:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.50,1:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,May I also have your picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.52,1:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.68,1:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Madison, I had a 34 Chevy coupe,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.95,1:07:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ran out of oil,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.75,1:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I threw a rod through the block.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.50,1:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It cost me 10 bucks to get it towed into Madison,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.80,1:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,where I sold it for junk for $5.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.99,1:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.83,1:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.10,1:07:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I finally got the guts to ask you a question,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.94,1:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,being the third time that I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.97,1:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.03,1:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.65,1:07:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.57,1:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But most of all, I'd like to ask Susan
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.55,1:07:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for having facilitated you coming out in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.23,1:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and teaching devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.31,1:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.53,1:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she gets enough credit for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.69,1:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, my question is...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.92,1:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, you lazy look, she said.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.78,1:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what got me going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.02,1:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weighing, what, 90 pounds or something back then?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.20,1:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.28,1:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is regarding a few meditation courses
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.94,1:08:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've taken in the last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.12,1:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're familiar with Vipassana meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.82,1:08:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Vipassana technically is the path to enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.69,1:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that took me to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.03,1:08:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That took the Buddha?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.44,1:08:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.28,1:08:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't heard that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.64,1:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.84,1:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know if Vipassana meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.82,1:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is aligned with my own spiritual journey,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.02,1:08:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.84,1:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the name of the meditation?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.50,1:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vipassana or Vipassana?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.14,1:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.84,1:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's several...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.72,1:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it begins with a V.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.40,1:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,V, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.02,1:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Vipassana.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.24,1:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.08,1:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.50,1:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.20,1:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask if we have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.48,1:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.30,1:09:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As taught by S.N. Goenka.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.76,1:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Vipassana.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.28,1:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Vipassana is aligned with your spiritual destiny, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.64,1:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is aligned and helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.70,1:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's aligned and helpful with your spiritual pathway, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.42,1:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.36,1:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.96,1:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.54,1:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.89,1:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.87,1:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.54,1:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.76,1:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Vipassana is a historical, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.02,1:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.29,1:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Vipassana, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.25,1:09:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.54,1:09:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he said bypassa.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.01,1:09:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bypassa the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.83,1:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, bypassa.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.90,1:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I said Pali words.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.04,1:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.60,1:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bypassa the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.74,1:10:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.70,1:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I just be with you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.48,1:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.50,1:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.53,1:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.01,1:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.48,1:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a boy who doesn't talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.37,1:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have to tell him to shut up and cut it short.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.46,1:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.32,1:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To facilitate awakening, I would like to know how to spend my time in the mornings.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.32,1:10:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wake up between four and five, and I have until about seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.10,1:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do centering prayer, Father Keating centering prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.34,1:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.34,1:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're following the centering prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.34,1:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.84,1:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.34,1:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Father Keating?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.84,1:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.34,1:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.84,1:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.34,1:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is doing that and doing Bible study, and then also Gurdjieff's The Fourth Way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.34,1:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.34,1:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading the work, and I just wondered, because the work seems so intellectual to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.84,1:11:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.34,1:11:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a little bit too much for what you're looking for, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.72,1:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Awakening.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.98,1:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Gurdjieff.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.98,1:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.36,1:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.36,1:11:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe not that, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.60,1:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gurdjieff may not be, let's see, I forget what Gurdjieff calibrates that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.60,1:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.34,1:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't need Gurdjieff on top of it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.34,1:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.34,1:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.34,1:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.90,1:11:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you get programmed to start looking in this direction, and then looking in that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.23,1:11:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.23,1:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.10,1:11:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working with just getting to the experience of, like, not labeling my
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.62,1:12:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,experience, the energy, like Gurdjieff . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.86,1:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call it anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.86,1:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be whatever it is, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.86,1:12:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And surrendering it, allowing it, and it's getting to . . . this has been going on for
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.12,1:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,years now, and it's getting to the point where I'm extremely uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.86,1:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncomfortable?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.86,1:12:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.86,1:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.86,1:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like my whole being is caught up in a taffy machine, churning, and tension, and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.62,1:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.62,1:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at this point of questioning the energy that I'm experiencing, whether it's something
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.39,1:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to release, or just to open up to, but at this . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.44,1:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let go resisting it, you'll disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.52,1:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.10,1:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My concern has been that when you talked about the ego . . . I mean, the . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.05,1:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.05,1:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,. . . the id today . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.05,1:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.05,1:13:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,. . . and the . . . all the dark aspects of humanity, that has been coming up at the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.25,1:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,same time with this, and I've been concerned about being run by that, and all the stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.69,1:13:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you've said about lower astral energies, too, and . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.77,1:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to give reality to them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.87,1:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reality that I have is whatever you give them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.77,1:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.08,1:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd give them any kind of . . . I wouldn't give them much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.08,1:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.46,1:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.46,1:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.29,1:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.48,1:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd give them much credence, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.48,1:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The flashing by, I wouldn't identify.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.41,1:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider them as an aspect of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.41,1:13:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.41,1:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just starting to . . . I feel like coming out of denial about a lot of the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.29,1:14:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,darker aspects . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.29,1:14:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the darker aspects.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.29,1:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.29,1:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.29,1:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are within the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.51,1:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.51,1:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.51,1:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The cingulate gyrus.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.58,1:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.58,1:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The cingulate gyrus calibrates about 170.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.58,1:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.58,1:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.58,1:14:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.58,1:14:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You give it enough flexibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.61,1:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The prefrontal cortex calibrates at 200, which is neutral, because that's the same as the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.34,1:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,human body, which is the same as the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.76,1:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The planet, the human body, the prefrontal cortex, are neutral.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.29,1:14:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.29,1:14:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good or bad, they just are, like a stone sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.33,1:14:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A stone is neither good nor bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.12,1:14:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those terms are not applicable to it, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.56,1:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.56,1:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's neither good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.17,1:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The cingulate gyrus is the gyrus in the brain
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.40,1:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the seat of animal instincts.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.14,1:14:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't call them evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.12,1:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just call them animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.23,1:15:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you have to ask yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.77,1:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,am I an animal or am I something beyond the animal
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.45,1:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and deny the reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.53,1:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can just let it rip.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.22,1:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you say, okay, animal, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.94,1:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not identical with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.66,1:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You, I have gone beyond.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.26,1:15:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're where I was a couple of million years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.51,1:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The dinosaur is in our id.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.60,1:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It loves to kill for the fun of killing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.21,1:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's where we were millions of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.51,1:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.53,1:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the daily course lessons.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.29,1:15:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And also I just feel a tremendous attraction
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.01,1:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,towards Zen type, Taoist Zen type teachings, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.81,1:15:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes I'll intensely go with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.81,1:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And recently in talking with a friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.01,1:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who I respect very much said,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.45,1:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, I'd be very careful
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.35,1:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Zen type style teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.51,1:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As he believes, like many teachers have fallen
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.71,1:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and who have followed that rote, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.99,1:16:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to get from you that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.89,1:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen always doesn't include pathway of the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.21,1:16:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and that type of thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.57,1:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I want to go on intensely,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.79,1:16:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is there any pitfalls or downfalls
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.59,1:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,one should watch out for
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.75,1:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if they totally just go for the,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.69,1:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the path of the heart?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.77,1:16:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I? Zen tip, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.74,1:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen style meditation?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.94,1:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.76,1:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what your main energy is put into?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.94,1:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if I totally just go with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.46,1:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this question is coming up
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.72,1:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just from a conversation with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.68,1:16:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a strong attraction towards Zen type teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.60,1:16:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and Taoism, Advaita, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.78,1:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.62,1:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.86,1:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Zen, Buddhism will not lead you into any evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.48,1:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You may transcend the void,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.26,1:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.09,1:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of Huang Po,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.73,1:17:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.01,1:17:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already heard to affirm the presence of God as love
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.97,1:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you'll transcend the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.05,1:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Zen is a very rapid and I like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.67,1:17:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a strict discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.09,1:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.75,1:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.65,1:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not okay, I'll beat you with a stick.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.49,1:17:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.01,1:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.17,1:17:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did Zen meditation for many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.24,1:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.25,1:17:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.89,1:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you for your presence in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.21,1:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.35,1:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My question today is about being too hard on myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.19,1:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.31,1:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to make good choices all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.35,1:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in alignment with my heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.37,1:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but hindsight is always 20-20.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.83,1:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.25,1:18:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tend to review past choices,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.41,1:18:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and be myself up for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.19,1:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, could you help me with self-forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.21,1:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't identify with that which you were in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.67,1:18:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you were at that time
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.53,1:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,made that choice because of that which you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.72,1:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you are not that anymore,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.98,1:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore, you negate that choice
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.10,1:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as being inappropriate for who you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.18,1:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably okay for that that you were then,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.66,1:18:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not okay for what you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.02,1:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't identify what was in the past
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.78,1:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.10,1:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with the reality of who you are now,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.18,1:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because who you were then no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.76,1:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a memory of a past state.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.99,1:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.79,1:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.41,1:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.87,1:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What you did in the past has to be looked at
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.83,1:19:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the context of who you were at the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.76,1:19:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you are now says it's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.26,1:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not who you were then.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.38,1:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you were then decided,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.95,1:19:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, he needed a good punch in the eye,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.69,1:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so you gave him a punch in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.08,1:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't do that now
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.50,1:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't need to prove
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.96,1:19:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can protect yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.44,1:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you're as strong as a man
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.92,1:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever the event was.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.92,1:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was okay for that,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.10,1:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever that person was then,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.66,1:19:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but that person no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.40,1:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't step into the same river twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.42,1:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.54,1:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different river now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.78,1:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Different river now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.94,1:19:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.84,1:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't choose it now
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.06,1:19:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's not who you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.94,1:19:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.82,1:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.19,1:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.39,1:19:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My love to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.57,1:19:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.31,1:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.91,1:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.55,1:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a good biff in the nose, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.16,1:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're 14,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.04,1:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to learn to give him a good biff in the nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.67,1:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At 80, it looks ridiculous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.86,1:20:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.02,1:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been following your work
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.56,1:20:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for about five or six years now,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.77,1:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel very privileged to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.61,1:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.12,1:20:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is that many spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.04,1:20:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,teach you to use a pendulum
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.53,1:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it taps into your brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.52,1:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It taps into the universal mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.78,1:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you clarify between the kinesiologic test
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.32,1:20:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the pendulum?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.36,1:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.52,1:20:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To use the pendulum to try to ascertain truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.79,1:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.99,1:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.29,1:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it useful?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.39,1:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.55,1:20:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The pendulum.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.49,1:20:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useful, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.22,1:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In your CDs, discovery CDs,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.02,1:20:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you say not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.06,1:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're hearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.12,1:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in some of your CDs, you use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.44,1:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because unless you're well taught,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.24,1:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,people start, they have to start
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.50,1:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,fishing around with negative energies.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.18,1:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing you do is you pick up a negative entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.76,1:21:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, you're being run by the negative entity,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.20,1:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're getting the exact opposite of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.02,1:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't go poking around trying to find out
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.16,1:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what is Hitler calibrated, Bin Laden,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.64,1:21:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.63,1:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.11,1:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So just use it for, to know truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.75,1:21:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To make decisions, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.49,1:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.42,1:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, make decisions.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.14,1:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help you make decisions.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.90,1:21:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.86,1:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only one of many, you know, ways of getting answers, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.53,1:21:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It may corroborate or not corroborate something that you wish to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.16,1:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, may I have your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.72,1:21:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, many people have found it useful, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.94,1:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.52,1:22:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, may I have your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.00,1:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, and stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.26,1:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay, I'm moving as fast as my widow Wicks can carry me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.96,1:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.16,1:22:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.30,1:22:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the preface to Power Vs. Force,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.36,1:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned upon reaching a certain level of awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.24,1:22:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that few follow the steps because they're so simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.60,1:22:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, why would few follow simple steps?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.10,1:22:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.84,1:22:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know, you say that the steps are very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.64,1:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.38,1:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The steps are very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.66,1:22:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What steps?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.42,1:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon reaching a certain level of awareness that you described.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.58,1:23:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Steps to enlightenment are very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.51,1:23:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.33,1:23:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's just a matter of willingness to do them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.37,1:23:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But he says, why don't more people follow it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.03,1:23:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how do I know?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.15,1:23:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their karmic destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.82,1:23:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are smarter than others.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.81,1:23:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people curse Walmarts and other people shop there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.97,1:23:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to save money?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.65,1:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on your motivation, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.02,1:23:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The steps in and of themselves are simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.95,1:23:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be a college graduate or an intellectual genius
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.39,1:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand the willingness to forgive people.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.41,1:23:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it, a willingness, a willingness to be loving towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.57,1:23:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to be a PhD or a genius to be willing to be gentle and loving
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.20,1:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and supportive of all of life and all of its expressions, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.36,1:23:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I say it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.15,1:24:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to memorize, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.30,1:24:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a willingness, a willingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.04,1:24:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a picture too?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.38,1:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a willingness, you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.24,1:24:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.04,1:24:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for all that you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.69,1:24:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My question relates to surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.27,1:24:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the difference between true surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.91,1:24:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and stuffing emotions, denying emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.71,1:24:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between surrender and what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.61,1:24:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,True surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.69,1:24:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stuffing, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.83,1:24:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuffing is refusing to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.81,1:24:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because I had a recent experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.37,1:24:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.95,1:24:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.51,1:24:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.47,1:24:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You just let the angriness be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.45,1:24:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry, angry, angry, angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.75,1:25:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After about midnight, the angriness gets very tiresome
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.55,1:25:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say, the hell with it, go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.34,1:25:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.60,1:25:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So then it can be more healthy to experience through that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.92,1:25:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than constantly saying, well, I surrender or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.64,1:25:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I've said before, those of us who remember,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.76,1:25:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, there's a number one stack, number two stack, number three stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.44,1:25:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's a mild stack, you can,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.56,1:25:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get over it in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.80,1:25:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a heavy stack, it'll take a repeated application of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.20,1:25:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But eventually, it runs out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.13,1:25:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.84,1:25:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.48,1:25:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.60,1:25:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it better to not discuss it among friends and family
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.58,1:25:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and that sort of a thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.42,1:25:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of their business.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.56,1:25:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So it's better because that lends to juicing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.18,1:25:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell them you're working through something.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.84,1:25:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to share it with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.98,1:25:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on how understanding they are, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.35,1:25:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Some families are sort of.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.39,1:26:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sort of idiotic when it comes to anything spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.59,1:26:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.15,1:26:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would look to them for forbearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.31,1:26:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.37,1:26:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And other people are more, you know, understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.50,1:26:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on how spiritually evolved the family itself is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.12,1:26:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's appropriate or not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.64,1:26:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.52,1:26:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can also explain it to people.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.67,1:26:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just you're working through a lot of angriness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.91,1:26:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See, if you're in therapy, you can always blame it on your therapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.04,1:26:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.54,1:26:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.12,1:26:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.78,1:26:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife sends her love and couldn't be here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.52,1:26:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.32,1:26:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.52,1:26:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.82,1:26:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.86,1:26:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a friend who is a Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.62,1:26:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've met him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.22,1:26:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monk in the Ramakrishna order.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.24,1:26:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He also.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.80,1:26:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.26,1:26:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.00,1:26:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.64,1:26:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're either too close or too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.20,1:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know which it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.72,1:26:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So my wife sends her love.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.66,1:26:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.74,1:26:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.62,1:26:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.74,1:26:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.32,1:26:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And a friend named Brian, who is a monk in the Ramakrishna order, asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.40,1:27:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.20,1:27:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to tell you thank you for all the work you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.02,1:27:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.30,1:27:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really came up here just to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.96,1:27:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.30,1:27:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm working on reading Nisargadatta's work on focusing meditation on I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.74,1:27:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.56,1:27:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you could say a little bit about that, I am, as a meditation, and
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.84,1:27:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about awareness tapping into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.08,1:27:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say much about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.24,1:27:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a technique that he advised.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.36,1:27:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.63,1:27:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.66,1:27:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it gets to be verbalized.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.52,1:27:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A repetition is verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.50,1:27:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.47,1:27:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness I seek is a nonverbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.50,1:27:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's of a nonverbal knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.32,1:27:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that you know about yourself is that you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.20,1:27:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is also true in philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.62,1:27:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.49,1:27:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, therefore, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.35,1:28:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ergo, I assume, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.01,1:28:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know that it's a really good phrase to repeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.65,1:28:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid with you it's going to become a phrase, and you're repeating this phrase over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.49,1:28:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.12,1:28:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say instead of who am I, look at what am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.98,1:28:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I is going to make you search around for another pronoun, more universal-sounding
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.64,1:28:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,pronoun, but still a pronoun.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.39,1:28:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think instead of who am I, I prefer what am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.04,1:28:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.32,1:28:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a what, not a who.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.56,1:28:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.24,1:28:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See, a who already makes you a separate individual pronoun identity.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.82,1:28:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A what is a far more generalized identity.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.92,1:28:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.34,1:28:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.48,1:28:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.56,1:28:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.64,1:28:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.68,1:28:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.84,1:28:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.90,1:28:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.92,1:28:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.28,1:28:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Explanation of the self with a capital S. Yeah. Mm-hmm. Yeah, okay. Thanks
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.47,1:29:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. What am I you reflect on that without using the words?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.82,1:29:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi suggested
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.27,1:29:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hi who I just had a question
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.54,1:29:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,lately, I feel like I have been I used to come in to the lectures and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.98,1:29:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it felt like my head was going to come off the top of my head was going to come off. It felt great
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.20,1:29:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt really in tune with everything and lately. I've just felt really flat
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.16,1:29:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And like I'm spinning my wheels and not going anyplace
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.78,1:29:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or doing anything so what now yeah, so what now?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.68,1:29:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.45,1:30:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you trying to program it or what am I trying to program it? Mm-hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.99,1:30:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I'm trying to figure out what to do spiritually because I feel like I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.50,1:30:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hanging around lots of resentment coming up always. I you know you mean as far as the process how to process
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.00,1:30:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit thing about spiritual processing yeah, yes, just what is I did the course of miracles a couple years
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.72,1:30:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I used to do every day, and now I don't worry about where do you go with meditation?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.86,1:30:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just look at the breath. Huh I watched the breath. Oh, you watch the breath yes. Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.21,1:30:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.25,1:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,take care of you for the next 20, 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.82,1:30:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.74,1:30:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a young man, you want to go
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.24,1:30:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,from Chicago to New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.66,1:30:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work that way, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.44,1:30:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay right in Chicago
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.82,1:30:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize more
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.42,1:30:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and more about who Chicago, what
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.34,1:30:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicago is and who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.18,1:30:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.60,1:30:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.92,1:31:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stay right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.54,1:31:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay right where I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.78,1:31:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A tent of an inch from exactly where
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.78,1:31:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you are and just
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.50,1:31:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,stay fixed there and refuse
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.88,1:31:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to budge. Refuse to
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.78,1:31:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,budge. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.56,1:31:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Insist on being just
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.30,1:31:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.87,1:31:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.69,1:31:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No evolving, no progressing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.68,1:31:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No evolving, no progressing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.28,1:31:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time I see you, just stay and do not move
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.62,1:31:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,one iota.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.63,1:31:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.17,1:31:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not asking much, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.61,1:31:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.67,1:31:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.69,1:31:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the answer he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.76,1:31:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.98,1:31:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.84,1:31:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move one iota
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.38,1:31:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.26,1:31:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No progress, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.82,1:31:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any accomplishments,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.88,1:31:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,any great awarenesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.94,1:31:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any great leaps of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.75,1:31:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.83,1:32:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise to not move an inch
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.75,1:32:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.19,1:32:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.85,1:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try and help him out with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.29,1:32:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me nervous to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.57,1:32:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.79,1:32:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.39,1:32:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been married
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.11,1:32:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,three months tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.63,1:32:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.55,1:32:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.04,1:32:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if you can speak at all
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.10,1:32:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to alignment versus involvement.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.90,1:32:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.28,1:32:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.30,1:32:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alignment versus involvement.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.44,1:32:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.58,1:32:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you could even...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.52,1:32:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean as a couple?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.02,1:32:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.46,1:32:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.78,1:32:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.42,1:32:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alignment is like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.62,1:32:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both headed in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.44,1:32:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.32,1:32:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.76,1:32:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no interference
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.06,1:32:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're both headed the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.76,1:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both trying to be as loving as you can
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.60,1:32:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and fulfill your obligation to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.58,1:32:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and society, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.04,1:33:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both heading in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.82,1:33:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.32,1:33:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.30,1:33:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.78,1:33:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the way most people get involved
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.64,1:33:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is there's a power struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.02,1:33:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes from one solar plexus to the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.92,1:33:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to do it my way?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.78,1:33:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to do it your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.08,1:33:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.08,1:33:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.94,1:33:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a lot of ads a lot of times
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.64,1:33:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that try to sell something.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.52,1:33:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it focuses on the guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.48,1:33:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and you hear what he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.30,1:33:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and it focuses on the woman,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.10,1:33:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and she winks and says,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.54,1:33:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he's going to do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.81,1:33:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a struggle for who's going to win,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.67,1:33:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to see things in terms of a struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.77,1:33:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,between one and the other,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.91,1:33:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,winning and losing, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.00,1:33:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See that you're both aligned,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.32,1:33:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then all you can discuss is how the two of you
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.08,1:33:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,can best get there together, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.18,1:33:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.72,1:33:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not hard to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.70,1:33:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I think he's cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.58,1:33:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.50,1:33:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.06,1:34:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not really sure how to do it, or myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.02,1:34:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.18,1:34:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.68,1:34:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, do you get into arguments?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.16,1:34:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.72,1:34:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you read the book?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.22,1:34:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're different.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.28,1:34:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.92,1:34:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's read.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.42,1:34:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read some of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.64,1:34:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you've got to read the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.90,1:34:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.16,1:34:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing is to realize if you both have the same goal,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.92,1:34:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're not interfering.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.30,1:34:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have different goals, different goals,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.98,1:34:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're going to cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.27,1:34:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You both want to have a job and buy a house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.07,1:34:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so you're aligned.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.11,1:34:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.23,1:34:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One says, no, I don't want to buy a house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.77,1:34:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get a horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.30,1:34:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to buy a racehorse.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.64,1:34:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, now you're going to have a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.70,1:34:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.46,1:34:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.50,1:34:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may be more general.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.84,1:34:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want is a satisfying home,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.60,1:34:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you discuss which would be the most satisfying home.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.14,1:35:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an RV versus a brick cottage, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.46,1:35:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's being too literal.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.88,1:35:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we just slip in and out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.32,1:35:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.82,1:35:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It just gets discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.86,1:35:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it takes some years to.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.08,1:35:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,More than three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.16,1:35:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.66,1:35:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it takes days.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.91,1:35:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.15,1:35:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets better all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.67,1:35:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The first year of marriage is tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.91,1:35:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets better all the time, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.33,1:35:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You get used to how to discuss things, how to discuss,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.53,1:35:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,how to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.42,1:35:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.92,1:35:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The marital discourse.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.76,1:35:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.01,1:35:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.14,1:35:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.26,1:35:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okey-doke.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.08,1:35:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.27,1:35:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.59,1:35:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.09,1:35:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.43,1:35:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.43,1:36:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time being here, and I'm from Seattle,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.77,1:36:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Washington.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.27,1:36:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys have any groups in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.79,1:36:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.79,1:36:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We have several groups in Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.04,1:36:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.11,1:36:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.11,1:36:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to consciousnessproject.org,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.11,1:36:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he has a list of all the groups and their locations.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.11,1:36:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.11,1:36:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.36,1:36:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.36,1:36:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come at a very pivotal time in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.00,1:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just honored to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.00,1:36:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what the most difficult period in anybody's life is called?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.00,1:36:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.00,1:36:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.00,1:36:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.16,1:36:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.16,1:36:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.16,1:36:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.16,1:36:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.90,1:36:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.90,1:36:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.02,1:36:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.02,1:36:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.02,1:36:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.02,1:36:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.02,1:36:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.02,1:36:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.02,1:36:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.02,1:36:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.02,1:36:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.02,1:36:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.02,1:36:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.02,1:36:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.02,1:36:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.42,1:36:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.69,1:36:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.69,1:36:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.69,1:36:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.79,1:36:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.79,1:36:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.64,1:36:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.29,1:36:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about you, but .
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.93,1:37:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.93,1:37:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.93,1:37:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.93,1:37:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor and a privilege to be here with
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.93,1:37:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.93,1:37:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned the angel when we cross over, when we drop the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.75,1:37:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was, because of past experience, it seemed
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.29,1:37:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was angelic guidance going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.34,1:37:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a trueism?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.12,1:37:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.52,1:37:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.68,1:37:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have your own spiritual guide,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.32,1:37:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,your own personal angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.26,1:37:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.06,1:37:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own personal angel guides.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.46,1:37:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.28,1:37:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice thought, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.58,1:37:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.22,1:37:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.06,1:37:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.80,1:37:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.16,1:37:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could ask for anything more?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.84,1:37:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not as cooperative, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.26,1:37:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for leading the way for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.86,1:38:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some really dark nights about four months ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.45,1:38:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and they turned into dark weeks,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.15,1:38:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which I can't recommend.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.92,1:38:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I attended a seminar in a state of fear,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.12,1:38:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel really guilty about being here in that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.94,1:38:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.87,1:38:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,also I'm grateful for the refuge,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.23,1:38:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for being able to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.09,1:38:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you can help me reconcile my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.91,1:38:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconcile what?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.77,1:38:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's torn up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.75,1:38:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels afraid, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.94,1:38:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an extreme state of fear during that dark night of soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.58,1:38:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear, dark night of soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.61,1:38:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.07,1:38:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was experiencing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.62,1:38:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to have a better description of the fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.00,1:38:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.27,1:38:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oblivion?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.53,1:38:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.35,1:38:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sin?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.05,1:38:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Death?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.24,1:39:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like an energy came in that shut down my third eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.22,1:39:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.64,1:39:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you kind of, I experienced,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.96,1:39:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was aware of what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.50,1:39:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was all these thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.66,1:39:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,attack thoughts flying around,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.66,1:39:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't really disassociate myself from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.35,1:39:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about being attacked by demons.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.49,1:39:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it appears.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.65,1:39:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.09,1:39:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about being attacked by demons.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.65,1:39:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.03,1:39:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.99,1:39:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you rebuked them and refused them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.95,1:39:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.43,1:39:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And denied them reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.81,1:39:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.59,1:39:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And demand that they leave you and get the hints.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.05,1:39:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.81,1:39:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.17,1:39:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.37,1:39:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came here in a state,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.15,1:39:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in the state,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.35,1:39:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel really,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.07,1:39:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel guilty about having been here in that state,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.97,1:39:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.21,1:39:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,like in the sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.09,1:39:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.13,1:39:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Catholic,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.25,1:39:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm born Catholic.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.22,1:39:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor lad.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.04,1:39:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.69,1:39:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.27,1:39:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharon Begora, the good Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.79,1:39:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,will forgive you for your good will.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.37,1:39:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.97,1:39:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.59,1:40:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can do six Hail Marys and the Rosary back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.13,1:40:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And a little donation to the church building fund
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.83,1:40:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,would be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.17,1:40:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.56,1:40:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.46,1:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.82,1:40:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.56,1:40:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.22,1:40:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.08,1:40:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.58,1:40:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.99,1:40:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.10,1:40:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.30,1:40:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come up and express my gratitude,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.13,1:40:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,my thanks,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.66,1:40:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,my admiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.72,1:40:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.22,1:40:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The love of the group that we work with in the Delaware Valley
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.33,1:40:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,could be an inspiration to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.68,1:40:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my children,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.26,1:40:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.90,1:40:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I also feel the part that is also me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.68,1:41:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was listening to a tape on the way up last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.52,1:41:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were saying that sometimes you feel like
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.90,1:41:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at myself through someone else's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.56,1:41:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.58,1:41:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.67,1:41:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, I just can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.13,1:41:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.84,1:41:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of the phenomena to develop on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.56,1:41:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets better all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.99,1:41:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.87,1:41:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.37,1:41:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.21,1:41:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you got to pull off the rope.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.09,1:41:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.23,1:41:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.13,1:41:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember having to pull off the rope.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.39,1:41:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.55,1:41:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.78,1:41:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.00,1:41:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first seminar.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.58,1:41:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.98,1:41:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been a great student of your work,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.50,1:41:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.30,1:41:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And, um,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.62,1:41:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd written down questions in reading your work from before,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.68,1:42:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't think of any for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.92,1:42:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll just say thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.09,1:42:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.49,1:42:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.73,1:42:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.21,1:42:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.75,1:42:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.06,1:42:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, these new-fangled gadgets.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.06,1:42:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.60,1:42:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.41,1:42:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.92,1:42:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come and talk to you about music.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.64,1:42:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.34,1:42:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Music.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.60,1:42:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.16,1:42:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Music is very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.08,1:42:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a music teacher for about six years in all my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.94,1:42:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, it's been a part of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.18,1:42:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.40,1:42:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that different things calibrate at different amounts.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.40,1:43:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And, um.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.30,1:43:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.82,1:43:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.80,1:43:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to ask you, um,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.64,1:43:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.82,1:43:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you where some things calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.06,1:43:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does jazz music calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.15,1:43:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you, uh, uh, there's a book called, uh, Truth Versus Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.45,1:43:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a section in Chapter 9, I think, on music.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.79,1:43:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.97,1:43:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All the various forms of music are calibrated there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.57,1:43:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the great musicians, uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.06,1:43:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.92,1:43:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And as far as instruments go, like an electric guitar with distortion,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.78,1:43:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,does that calibrate high?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.91,1:43:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I never calibrated individual instruments, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.73,1:43:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.97,1:43:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's what you put into them.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.87,1:43:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the instrument itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.55,1:43:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put all your heart and soul in it, and wow, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.04,1:43:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.38,1:43:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so it's what you put into music.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.02,1:43:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all music is great, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.04,1:43:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All music is great, except for rap music and that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.84,1:43:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.86,1:43:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary's Less Than 200 is demonic, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.60,1:43:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.14,1:43:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, raping and killing and shooting and stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.94,1:43:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.86,1:44:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.56,1:44:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.63,1:44:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the black singer that sings,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.15,1:44:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful world?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.89,1:44:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.19,1:44:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Louis Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.08,1:44:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Louis Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.74,1:44:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary's the highest of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.68,1:44:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Five centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.18,1:44:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful world.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.00,1:44:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Calvary's, I think, is the highest of all the pop singers.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.66,1:44:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I just have one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.06,1:44:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If we as a group are here to serve God and mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.31,1:44:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how do we accept the downfall or the,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.84,1:44:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what consciousness, level of consciousness is happening now?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.92,1:44:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In our society and in our culture?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.92,1:44:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.92,1:45:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the normal fluctuations of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.92,1:45:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution's not a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.01,1:45:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it goes like this, and it goes like this, and then, you know, it goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.01,1:45:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it has big advances, and then it slides back, and then it goes forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.32,1:45:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the dark ages were very dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.32,1:45:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark ages were very dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.32,1:45:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have the high of the ancient Greek intellectual Plato, and Sophocles, and Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.67,1:45:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from the greatest, and then it declines, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.96,1:45:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you have the Renaissance, the renewal, the Protestant Revolution, you know, the Renaissance in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.85,1:45:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The rebirth of what was already known in ancient Greece but had been forgotten, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.24,1:45:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these are normal fluctuations, you know, in the growth curve.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.24,1:45:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes what happens is you don't have the impetus to bounce further until you hit bottom,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.91,1:46:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you say, that's enough of that, and then you turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.91,1:46:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're trying to see how, you know, what gains are there in falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.10,1:46:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're plumbing the depths.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.42,1:46:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How far will falsehood get you?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.42,1:46:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to find out that it doesn't get us too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.68,1:46:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To be an apologist for evil, you join in the karmic consequences of that evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.39,1:46:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the apologists for evil will hit their own skids, and then there'll be a turnaround again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.67,1:46:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.80,1:46:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes like so, like waves.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.37,1:46:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you trace it over history, you see the energy field of mankind goes up and down and down.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.66,1:46:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine providence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.35,1:46:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we only learn by mistakes, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.41,1:47:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we check this out, and we see where it leads us, and then we say, oh, I see where that leads us, so we'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.59,1:47:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Libertinism, well, brings you to a bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.16,1:47:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hit that bottom, you come back up again.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.64,1:47:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You reminded me of Wayne Dyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.66,1:47:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you said Wayne Dyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.66,1:47:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.66,1:47:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.66,1:47:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I like your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.66,1:47:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there were more pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.82,1:47:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish that?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.82,1:47:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was more pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.82,1:47:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see the pictures there?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.13,1:48:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That plant used to belong to friends of yours, Bill and Lois Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.42,1:48:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.42,1:48:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-six years ago when Bill died, Lois passed along some of her plants
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.42,1:48:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to friends of theirs they sponsored in the AA, and she said to pass them on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.42,1:48:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be nice to see one come full circle since you were there when he died.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.42,1:48:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.00,1:48:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks just like Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.08,1:48:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks, that was a great gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.25,1:48:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill was a great being.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.21,1:48:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Changed the face of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.21,1:48:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Changed the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.21,1:48:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate the impact of the various religions.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.70,1:48:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On American society today, you'll find that the one that calibrates the highest is the 12-step movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.76,1:49:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the greatest positive impact on our society.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.36,1:49:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can't answer all the questions because they're going to throw us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.36,1:49:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Run faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.36,1:49:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Their little legs are moving too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.74,1:49:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.08,1:49:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We closed the questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.08,1:49:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.56,1:49:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.56,1:49:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.72,1:49:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason nobody's there is because there's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.72,1:49:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.72,1:49:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.64,1:49:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they think?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.87,1:49:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who cut it off?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.54,1:49:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cut it off?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.79,1:49:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we got cut off.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.79,1:49:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.56,1:49:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.16,1:49:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, we give thanks for this magnificent day and the joy of thy presence as these people here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.20,1:50:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We give thanks for thy divine presence and inspiration, and I ask for thy blessing on this group.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.20,1:50:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We come in together, and we go out together.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.32,1:50:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We shift from this domain to the next domain, and then we flock back again in this domain,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.32,1:50:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we flock out again in that domain, and gradually we circle up and up and up and
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.32,1:50:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,up, up and up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.51,1:50:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then anyone's left here are the laggards.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.56,1:50:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we thank thee, O Lord, for the blessing of thy divine love, thy presence, for you
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.56,1:50:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.56,1:50:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.56,1:50:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank God for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.56,1:50:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.56,1:50:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.56,1:50:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.63,1:50:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.63,1:51:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm spoiled rotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.14,1:51:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.14,1:51:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.14,1:51:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.30,1:51:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a great and wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.30,1:51:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.30,1:51:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.61,1:51:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a blessed moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.61,1:51:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.61,1:54:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible group of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.04,1:54:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.08,1:54:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible group.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.08,1:54:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.08,1:54:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly blessed.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.46,1:54:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly blessed beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.24,1:54:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.24,1:55:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.43,1:55:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.43,1:55:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.52,1:55:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
